# EmailJS Configuration
# Get these values from https://www.emailjs.com/
# 1. Sign up for a free account at emailjs.com
# 2. Create an email service (e.g., Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# 3. Create an email template with these variables: {{from_name}}, {{from_email}}, {{message}}, {{to_email}}
# 4. Copy your Public Key, Service ID, and Template ID

VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
